That alone covers 95% of questions.

‚ùå COMMON WRONG ASSUMPTIONS

‚ùå mail sends immediately
‚úî deliver_now / deliver_later sends

‚ùå View must be passed explicitly
‚úî Auto-mapped by method name

üß™ QUICK PRACTICE (ANSWER IN YOUR HEAD)

